# URL the contact form will POST to. Leave unset during development —
# submissions will just be logged to the server console and the form
# will still show a success state.
#
# Point this at whatever you're using to receive leads, e.g.:
#   - A Formspree/Basin form endpoint
#   - A Zapier/Make webhook
#   - Your CRM's inbound webhook
#   - A Resend "send email" proxy endpoint
SCHEDULE_CALL_WEBHOOK_URL=
